name: complex_with_if_bound_max_branch
section: binding-order
args: a:Int b:Int fallback:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Binding min and max must make the greater-or-equal branch choose the max value.
law: (= (with [lo (fuzz-min {a} {b}) hi (fuzz-max {a} {b})] (if (fuzz-gte? hi lo) hi {fallback})) (fuzz-max {a} {b}))
